HEADWORD: Housewarming
<hw>House"warm`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A feast or
merry-making made by or for a family or business firm on taking
possession of a new house or premises.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
